                        <interp inst="t18350615-1605-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 31<hi rend="italic">.—Recommended to mercy by the Prosecutor.</hi>
               </p>
